{"type": "article", "id": 11534, "title": "极简化波斯地毯", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-02T11:00:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607115137K7a5vcOxmzGb9hpf.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t还记得之前那个用瓷器、石头和木材做<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/display/articles/10889.html\" target=\"_blank\">收纳容器</a>的法国设计师 Samuel Accoceberry 么，他最近推出的这一款波斯地毯也颇受好评。地毯整体采用极简的抽象设计风格，设计灵感来自古老的波斯图案，但与古典的繁复不同的是，他把传统花纹们简化成了一个个抽象的图形，使之更具体现代化的风格。材料上采用天然羊毛，保证质感。Samuel Accoceberry 在家具设计上善于使用明亮的颜色和舒适的材质，风格优雅，这是<a href=\"http://www.samuelaccoceberry.com/en\" target=\"_blank\">他的个人主页</a>，可以查看他更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135650g4DvEG9o2Ta5QJc3.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"470\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.48958333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135651cjWnIlHT6FOkDYyu.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"876\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.9125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135651g9nSs8lj6wcXRGP1.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"455\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.47395833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135652nQAYfHh0oxlFJVI9.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135652xuJ4GgQo16py5cZK.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.753125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135653u4dfy2DQ5tChEw67.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"633\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.659375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}